data.description: Welcome to this fantastic Dania Beach duplex! Each of the two updated 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom units boasts its own AC system and separate electric meters, offering flexibility for investors and homeowners alike. With carport parking for up to 2 vehicles per unit, this property is incredibly convenient. Plus, its location is unbeatable, just 3 miles from Fort Lauderdale Airport, 3.5 miles from Dania Beach Pier, and 2 miles from Oakwood Plaza. Don't miss your chance to own this gem in sunny Florida.  Please Review brokers Remarks for showing Requests
